00:17:36,823 --> 00:17:38,340
Hi, sweetie.

343
00:17:38,908 --> 00:17:43,318
I haven't seen you before.
You here for the wedding?

344
00:17:43,319 --> 00:17:46,748
No. I'm just here to listen to you.

